{"tid":1555366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請讓捐款成為習慣","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T13:31:08.000Z","uid":108676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef92599a6c8c5b88d044bff2ef6b6a2aed5ca86","tid":1555366,"uid":108676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"自反送中運動爆發以來<br />\n有多位前線手足被濫捕 、施虐<br />\n大家都係有目共睹<br />\n<br />\n被捕既手足長路漫漫<br />\n日後要面對複雜既司法程序同長期既監禁<br />\n極度需要各位支持<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動係一場持久戰<br />\n除左前線既勇武抗暴 鍵盤戰士既文宣外<br />\n亦需要照顧被捕手足既生活<br />\n唔好睇少自己 每一分每一毫 都非常重要<br />\n請讓捐款成為習慣 (612人道支援基金/ 星火同盟)<br />\n只有持續捐款 先可以令被迫害既手足日後有所依靠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n先貼為敬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYSO4Rt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYSO4Rt.jpg&h=846b7449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b92929f1f10a402c1e0d6dc3eb920181963c1138","tid":1555366,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f11dd36ef36658a855bab4aecd295094eee14f6","tid":1555366,"uid":108676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}